summary: This puts an Eye of Magnus back in the college for aesthetic reasons.
descriptionHtml:
This mod will add a duplicate of the Eye Of Magnus to the Hall of Elements. it has been place high to avoid having to move lights around. Not lore friendly, meant for aesthetic purposes. screenshots and what not. or just because you like the College quest line and want a souvenir.

The mod IS NOT QUEST AWARE! it will be enabled as soon as you enable the mod.

also included is a file adding one to the exterior courtyard of the college. use one or both.

Textures in the screenshot are from this mod:http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54965/
author: Dracula420
